{"tid":2108851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「In US, We trust」Moderna:新冠疫苗初期人體測試效果佳","createTime":"2020-07-15T00:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T01:15:00.000Z","uid":108201,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"edd29c6669530e81d0a1bbca907d36b9c74b7b28","tid":2108851,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T00:11:43.000Z","msg":"美國生化科技公司莫德納(Moderna)本月底將展開新冠病毒疫苗後期人體測試，集團最新披露，初期人體測試數據顯示，所有獲注射mRNA-1273疫苗的病人都安全，並且都有產生抗體，反映疫苗效果良好。<br />\n<br />\n消息曝光後，Moderna市後時段股價急升16%。<br />\n<br />\nModerna周二較早時公布，將於本月27日展開疫苗後期人體測試，對3萬人展開注射及研究。<br />\n<br />\nModerna其後在《新英格蘭醫學雜誌》(New England Journal of Medicine)發表研究報告，表示初期人體測試時，全部45個病人經過兩輪注射後，均產生免疫抗體，沒有人感到嚴重不適，只有半數人有輕微不適，結果令人鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\nModerna成為首個就疫苗進行人體測試的生化藥廠，5月公布初期人體測試初步結果，當時未有提交數據，資料也未經外間評審。"},{"pid":"4415b9fa864316c489ae2c587500a3d4ae04abce","tid":2108851,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9880b968f5b53eb0af1004a7a9f069d81cdbdc1a","tid":2108851,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"今日股票升係因為依個news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84954e8c3f96295c61d787fbc59a1029b3abb349","tid":2108851,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa155e645fffff8e80323bb9bc5f4377a95122e4","tid":2108851,"uid":63669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾Moderna，由年頭吹到年尾，其實乜叉都無研究到，純粹出口術炒高自己股價"},{"pid":"7d40312d2f8cabe1b3ec7bf89c94ab1f63548417","tid":2108851,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":1,